{"tid":2211632,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"蜜蜂喺生物之中算唔算屈","createTime":"2020-09-21T08:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T11:48:28.000Z","uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d09312c3275f8308071f6d029594c8008d4b4932","tid":2211632,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:55:26.000Z","msg":"佢地生存得好有方向好有目標<br />\n<br />\n幼蟲<br />\n餵蜂王漿變蜂后<br />\n餵蜂蜜變工蜂<br />\n變工蜂之後每個階段又負責唔同嘅工種<br />\n<br />\n保育蜂是剛完成羽化後不久的工蜂，其主要職責是飼養幼蟲；羽化約十天之後，其蠟腺開始分泌蜂蠟，此時的工蜂稱為築巢蜂，負責維護蜂巢並或清掃蜂巢中的垃圾和死蜂。羽化三周後，工蜂蠟腺停止分泌，此時工蜂將成為專職的采蜜蜂。<br />\n<br />\n反觀人類雖然好自由<br />\n但係好多人生存左幾十年都唔知自己喺度做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f969988a9f2cfa1f3274fac98617dbe9bdbce4","tid":2211632,"uid":110202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"我都想有用D<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e3058d1ac3d1d2fce71a69194244d665b1961c","tid":2211632,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"有時我覺得蜜蜂真係共產到爆"},{"pid":"0e3b502733e808f48b6c82c7400c7a806b78d789","tid":2211632,"uid":171273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6cf0f525de078e0c7baba35711ae5441384e693","tid":2211632,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e3058d1ac3d1d2fce71a69194244d665b1961c","tid":2211632,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"有時我覺得蜜蜂真係共產到爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"佢地點解知道自己要做啲咩野<br />\n係佢地啲ching教定係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098062cf11f2376e7bcf4c30753238766fd85f04","tid":2211632,"uid":165665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:10:01.000Z","msg":"呢啲嘢 你睇佢好 佢睇你好嘅姐<br />\n家家有本難唸的經"},{"pid":"6cf25fe8f084b0a128ac46d92d9dfdec76764cce","tid":2211632,"uid":29880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e3058d1ac3d1d2fce71a69194244d665b1961c","tid":2211632,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"有時我覺得蜜蜂真係共產到爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"其實共產主義對一個群體黎講係完美<br />\n但人類唔係完美"},{"pid":"09a78d5b75115f02864ffd14d257fc4793a66d0d","tid":2211632,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"0失業率生物唔係浪得虛名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人用過蜜蜂嚟比較人類，反而發覺人類正因為唔知做咩好所以生命先對自己有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蜜蜂一出生就fix咗條路"},{"pid":"7b586b345714cb0b9a0c32d806327935e158871b","tid":2211632,"uid":98624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf25fe8f084b0a128ac46d92d9dfdec76764cce","tid":2211632,"uid":29880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e3058d1ac3d1d2fce71a69194244d665b1961c","tid":2211632,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"有時我覺得蜜蜂真係共產到爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"其實共產主義對一個群體黎講係完美<br />\n但人類唔係完美"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"人類無辦法做到真正既共產啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072e3071e53fba2ccadbe8d9a614f05a7b45ce62","tid":2211632,"uid":38533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:11:51.000Z","msg":"年年都總有幾隻飛入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毅力驚人"},{"pid":"5a5d147fdcd7987a36208ea635c9acfba9d870b7","tid":2211632,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"其實係得樓豬你唔知想做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好拉全人類落水"},{"pid":"48a7f60cd212881c1f6bbcf4b4f69002e4b40a74","tid":2211632,"uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:15:20.000Z","msg":"其實蜜蜂一個群集可以睇成一個單獨既生命體<br />\n依個觀點係自私的基因入面有詳述過"},{"pid":"672caaf50139e3599957dc2e8ff3e9d29a5396f3","tid":2211632,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"社會一早assign左奴才既身份俾所有下層結構既人<br />\n目標好清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為做人類做乜都得實在太天真<br />\n淨係而家你網上講句「光復.....」都唔得啦<br />\n國安隨時拍門<br />\n<br />\n今日又話派錢俾新移民<br />\n你幾時見過有隻甲由走入蜂群會有蜜蜂養埋佢？<br />\n冇丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌！"},{"pid":"8ab7a79574d0c2afe7531fa50986712ba5f1d74c","tid":2211632,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6cf0f525de078e0c7baba35711ae5441384e693","tid":2211632,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e3058d1ac3d1d2fce71a69194244d665b1961c","tid":2211632,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"有時我覺得蜜蜂真係共產到爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"佢地點解知道自己要做啲咩野<br />\n係佢地啲ching教定係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:54:53.000Z","msg":"聽講係蜂后生蛋陣嗰啲安排佢哋嘅生理結構(社會地位)。<br />\n<br />\n當蜂后安排粒蛋冇受精就會生隻雄蜂，咁雄蜂就會白食白住直到成年繁殖期就飛出去交配然後屌閪屌到死<br />\n<br />\n如果係受精卵就生出雌蜂，佢哋當中大部份冇食開蜂皇漿，咁性器官作發展唔到冇生殖能力就變咗工蜂(勞動階層)，相反少部份食蜂皇漿由細食到大性器官正常就變咗後生蜂后(黨委幹部)<br />\n<br />\n到咗繁殖期仲興奮，舊嘅蜂后會帶少少馬仔自動離場另起爐灶。新嗰批後生蜂后就開始權鬥，死剩果一隻蜂后就成為蜂巢唯一統治者，然後先飛出去交配儲定晒啲精液就正式承繼蜂巢嘅生育業務。"},{"pid":"c3291e6e8e16f9e2cdfc134b2451130ec056a235","tid":2211632,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e3058d1ac3d1d2fce71a69194244d665b1961c","tid":2211632,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"有時我覺得蜜蜂真係共產到爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"共產係好野黎<br />\n只係人性限制左人類冇辦法做到"},{"pid":"9ba4d1d3e